          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The yield       curve       of      the      reaction",
                " Al-27(gamma,n)Al-26(m)  has   been   determined   by",
                " measuring the short-lived positron activity from the",
                " first excited state of 26Al.",
                "Analysis of  the  yield  curve by the least structure",
                " method reveals a cross section consistent with,  but",
                " with  more detail than previous measurements,  there",
                " being at least 14 resonances between  threshold  and",
                " 23  MeV.  Consistency  is shown to exist between the",
                " energies of this peaks and  the  energies  of  those",
                " found in photoneutron and photoproton energy spectra",
                " from 27Al reported from other laboratories.",
                "The reaction  threshold  is  found  to be 13.27(0.05)",
                " MeV.",
                "The integrated cross section from threshold to 25 MeV",
                " is found to be 31(5) MeV*mb.",
                "Interpretation of the cross section is discussed."
              ]
            }
          ],
